    "paragraphs": [
        {
            "style": "Text",
            "text": "A counter keeps track of how many instances of certain objects have come to existâ€”or have taken a certain valueâ€”during the duration of a certain context.",
            "updated": 1611259349617
        },
        {
            "style": "Text",
            "text": "For example, how many positions have been open during an episode, or how many of those positions have been hits."
        },
        {
            "style": "Text",
            "text": "Counters are kept in multiple contexts simultaneously. In particular, you will find episode counters, strategy counters, position counters, and order counters."
